OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FInflation rate eases but   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstill near 40-year high    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK inflation rate has eased        
OL,6, slightly although prices are still     
OL,7, continuing to rise at nearly their     
OL,8, fastest rate in 40 years.              
OL,10,FInflation - a measure of price rises - 
OL,11,Fdipped to 9.9% in the 12 months to     
OL,12,FAugust, from 10.1% in July, the Office 
OL,13,Ffor National Statistics (ONS) said.    
OL,15,FSoaring living costs are eating into   
OL,16,Fhousehold budgets, with prices rising  
OL,17,Ffaster than wages.                     
OL,19,FThe Bank of England has said inflation 
OL,20,Fcould peak at more than 13% this year. 
